name: Blue-Footed Booby
description: Everyone loves BOOBY, the cheeky Blue-footed bird on Base. With its striking blue feet and a laser focus on community, Booby is here to make you laugh with its booby meme factory with animated wonders, illustrations, and pure comedic gold. BOOBY empowers its top holders to steer the marketing wallet through governance voting. Embrace, hold it tight and let's FREE THE BOOBY!
